    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4c.34.14-15_0001" />
                
               <fw type="letterhead">
                Skyrim Farm                    <hi rend="caps">JOHN G. NEIHARDT</hi>
                   <lb/>
                Route 7
                   <lb/>
                Columbia, Mo.  
               </fw>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">14</fw>
                
                <opener>
                <dateline>Nov. 1st, '61</dateline> 
                
                
                <salute>Dear Slade:</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>I've been thinking of you more than usual for some reason or other, and I just feel moved to say hello and get a little closer to you.</p>
                
                <p>So Hello!</p>
                
                <p>Nothing new here. Things go well at the University. Test tomorrow, but I have nothing to do. My assistant is a whale and he has two procters to help him. My Poetry class is at least average &#8212; maybe a little better. They
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4c.34.14-15_0002"/>
                <fw type="authorial"><unclear>-</unclear>2-</fw>
                    <fw type="curatorial">15</fw>
                
                <hi rend="underline">work</hi>.</p>
                
                <p>What is the latest about your <hi rend="caps">M. S.</hi>?</p>
                <closer>
                <salute>The same old affection for you and Nita</salute>
                
                <signed>John.</signed>
                </closer>
                
                <postscript>
                <p>Did I send you a copy of the new <hi rend="underline">Black Elk Speaks</hi>? <hi rend="underline">Do</hi> you want a copy of the new printing of the <hi rend="underline">Cycle</hi>?</p>
                <closer>
                <signed>Jno.</signed>
                </closer>
                </postscript>
                
                
            </div1>
        </body>
        
